{"tid":585532,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG] 水上活動gp (sailing / windsurfing / kayaking / others)","createTime":"2018-03-08T17:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T14:32:23.000Z","uid":89469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"979a882696370b2de3acfdb10276df8cd9109320","tid":585532,"uid":89469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T17:44:04.000Z","msg":"[TG] 水上活動gp (sailing / windsurfing / kayaking / others)<br />\n<br />\n最近天氣開始轉熱了<br />\n又係玩水上活動既季節<br />\n<br />\n我岩岩學玩(sailing, kayaking)<br />\n康民抽到2046都未有位，包班去學又好難自己湊夠人<br />\n所以想開個新gp<br />\n當係比大家夾下人包班又好，分享下技術又好，組團去log鐘練習又好<br />\n希望之後大家學夠級可以一齊出下旅程玩下，本地又好外地又好<br />\n<br />\n除左以上活動(sailing / windsurfing / kayaking)<br />\n有玩開或對其他水上活動有興趣既，都可以入黎分享下<br />\n其他水上活動我冇乜研究唔知點去入門，所以只list左康民基本果三項<br />\n<br />\n歡迎有玩過 或 未玩過但有興趣既人加入<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/upwatersports\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fupwatersports&d=j8fWcMnyvWmOeCNNUtYcwDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=7917f117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/upwatersports</a>"},{"pid":"e6baac945a683c447df87010d222ddf34a756354","tid":585532,"uid":89469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75e976a9889dc4622c19ad0a77506e88c3efcc8","tid":585532,"uid":89469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T13:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ee2dd0d09bede4962cdc73f9520356c1fe6454","tid":585532,"uid":89469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ddd7b8817df1cfa45a821c1f12b411b1ba9645b","tid":585532,"uid":89469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T14:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid